title: Watch Video (4 in 1): YouTube Vimeo DailyMotion [Android - APK]
description:
Watch video from YouTube, Vimeo, Dailymotion and your local video. All within one app!.

- Do not require a login to YouTube, Vimeo, Dailymotion.
- Add to bookmark any channels, categories, related video and comments.
- Total local playlists, manage and reorder video in the playlists.
- Search videos and channels.
- Last viewed video.
- Categories.

Google Play Link: 
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.livecodedev.watchvideo
